Poulter, who turned professional in 1996, is a member of the world's top two professional golf tours, the U.S.-based PGA Tour and the European Tour.

In 2010, he won the WGC-Accenture Match Play Championship, before scooping the title in the WGC-HSBC Champions two years later.

